*Helm* is the successor of [[Anything]]. It's a generic framework for quickly accessing stuff within Emacs. Or: an "incremental completion and selection narrowing framework for Emacs."

* Source [https://github.com/emacs-helm/helm available from GitHub]
* Documentation on its own [https://github.com/emacs-helm/helm/wiki Helm Wiki]
* [http://tuhdo.github.io/helm-intro.html This article is a nice introduction to Helm's many features]

Other packages:

* HelmSwoop -- like [OccurMode occur], but /live/
